fire blade.name: Fire Blade
fire blade.desc: Release a slash of flames downwards that deals heavy posture damage.

reqs.from: Shares a cooldown with other Blades except for Lightning Blade.

flame repulsion.name: Flame Repulsion
flame repulsion.desc: Charge up an exertion of flames that knocks opponents backwards. If you take damage while charging, you repulse it back.

burning servants.name: Burning Servants
burning servants.desc: Summon a legion of flaming spearmen that lunge inwards.

fire gun.name: Fire Gun
fire gun.desc: Shoot successive bullets of fire from your fingertips.

flame grab.name: Flame Grab
flame grab.desc: Jet forwards with flames and slam anyone you catch in your clutches.

reqs.from: Shares a cooldown every other grab.

flame blind.name: Flame Blind
flame blind.desc: Shoot a projectile that explodes after a short delay and blinds those looking at it.

flame of denial.name: Flame Of Denial
flame of denial.desc: While active, you get right back up after being knocked.

fire forge.name: Fire Forge
fire forge.desc: Conjure flaming daggers and throw them forwards.

searing snare.name: Searing Snare
searing snare.desc: Place a fiery snare at a chosen location. Enemies that stumble into it are scorched.

graceful flame.name: Graceful Flame
graceful flame.desc: Conjure a campfire for you and your comrades to rest by.

relentless flames.name: Relentless Flames
relentless flames.desc: Bear down on your foes with repeated fiery slashes.

flare volley.name: Flare Volley
flare volley.desc: Conjure up to 3 fireballs to volley at your enemies.

flame leap.name: Flame Leap
flame leap.desc: Leap up leaving behind a burst of flames. Those nearby are dragged up too.

flame assault.name: Flame Assault
flame assault.desc: Dash forward in a spiral of flames.

flame ballista.name: Flame Ballista
flame ballista.desc: Conjure a flaming arrow and fire it at your target.

flaming scourge.name: Flaming Scourge
flaming scourge.desc: Conjure a flaming whip and sling your foes around and into the ground with a devastating slam.

ash slam.name: Ash Slam
ash slam.desc: Strike the ground, turning it to ash.

reqs.from: Shares a cooldown with other Blades except for Fire Blade.
Shares a cooldown every other grab.

electro carve.name: Electro Carve
electro carve.desc: Produce a highly potent field of electromagnetism, shocking all inside.

lightning impact.name: Lightning Impact
lightning impact.desc: Slam those under you with a lightning empowered kick.

lightning clones.name: Lightning Clones
lightning clones.desc: Replicated forms of yourself conjured from electricity.

lightning strike.name: Lightning Strike
lightning strike.desc: A strike of thunder at your desired location.

thunder kick.name: Thunder Kick
thunder kick.desc: An unrelenting kick like a clap of thunder.

fleeting sparks.name: Fleeting Sparks
fleeting sparks.desc: Call forth notes of electricity that seek out your foes.

storm blades.name: Storm Blades
storm blades.desc: Call forth a ring of blades to strike your enemies with furious lightning.

rising thunder.name: Rising Thunder
rising thunder.desc: Rise up with your opponent and crash down as a bolt of lightning.

emotion wave.name: Emotion Wave
emotion wave.desc: Conjure up surging waves of lightning that travel along the ground.

spark swap.name: Spark Swap
spark swap.desc: Almost instantaneous swap of location with whoever your cursor is on.

lightning cloak.name: Lightning Cloak
lightning cloak.desc: A lightning cloak that empowers you.

reqs.from: Shares a cooldown with Ice Lance.

gale punch.name: Gale Punch
gale punch.desc: Form a punch of wind in your fist and release it.

wind forge.name: Wind Forge
wind forge.desc: Encircle your foes with blades of wind that halt their escape until they respond.

twister kicks.name: Twister Kicks
twister kicks.desc: Go forth with spinning kicks infused with the wind.

champion's whirlthrow.name: Champion's Whirlthrow
champion's whirlthrow.desc: Grab your opponent and toss them with the power of gale.

rising wind.name: Rising Wind
rising wind.desc: Use wind to uppercut and propel yourself into the air. Press F after hitting an opponent to impale them.

wind carve.name: Wind Carve
wind carve.desc: A quick swirl of sharp winds.

astral wind.name: Astral Wind
astral wind.desc: A rapid delivery of consecutive attacks.

pillars of erisia.name: Pillars of Erisia
pillars of erisia.desc: Gaining inspiration from the Duke of Erisia, call forth a malicious gale from your stomp.

ice daggers.name: Ice Daggers
ice daggers.desc: Form and toss daggers of ice at your aimed opponent.

reqs.from: Shares a cooldown with other Blades.

ice forge.name: Ice Forge
ice forge.desc: Conjure and throw weapons of ice.

reqs.from: Shares a cooldown every other grab.

ice lance.name: Ice Lance
ice lance.desc: Form an icy spear and lunge forward.

reqs.from: Shares a cooldown with Gale Lunge.

rising frost.name: Rising Frost
rising frost.desc: Conjure a glaive of frost to launch your opponents skywards.

crystal knee.name: Crystal Knee
crystal knee.desc: Knock your enemy skyward with a kick of crystal.

crystal impale.name: Crystal Impale
crystal impale.desc: Impale your foes with a brutal crystal smash.

ice flock.name: Ice Flock
ice flock.desc: Send forth a flock of ice.

ice fissure.name: Ice Fissure
ice fissure.desc: Send ice rippling out in a shockwave.

ice cubes.name: Ice Cubes
ice cubes.desc: Manifest cubes of Ice to fire at your enemies. Cast mantra again to fire cubes.

ice skate.name: Ice Skate
ice skate.desc: Skate freely on paths of ice.

reqs.from: Shares a cooldown with other Blades.

shadow gun.name: Shadow Gun
shadow gun.desc: An awful blast of dark energy.

shadow seekers.name: Shadow Seekers
shadow seekers.desc: Call forth the void to track your opponents.

shade devour.name: Shade Devour
shade devour.desc: Gorge on your own health for raw strength.

encircle.name: Encircle
encircle.desc: Conjure shadows around your enemy before warp-striking to them.

devouring eye.name: Devouring Eye
devouring eye.desc: Summon a fragile eye that consumes the ether of those who try to cast mantras within it's gaze.

shade step.name: Shade Step
shade step.desc: Submerge into your shadow. Click to launch an attack at any point while sumberged.

reqs.from: Shares a cooldown with Beast Burrow and Sanguine Dive

shade bringer.name: Shade Bringer
shade bringer.desc: Temporarily summon a shadow greatsword for a large slash.

shadow vortex.name: Shadow Vortex
shadow vortex.desc: Create a shadow vortex that pulls in everything in its surroundings.

reqs.from: Shares a cooldown with Strong Left.

metal eruption.name: Metal Eruption
metal eruption.desc: The user stomps on the ground, and spawns a fury of metal spikes

metal rampart.name: Metal Rampart
metal rampart.desc: Form a medium size pillar at the user location .

metal kick.name: Metal Kick
metal kick.desc: A powerful kick laced with metal.

chain pull.name: Chain Pull
chain pull.desc: Conjure a chain to pull your opponent.

iron skin.name: Iron Skin
iron skin.desc: Upon use you coat your skin with a dark-ironlike substance, negating 75% of damage taken during the mantra's use.

metal rain.name: Metal Rain
metal rain.desc: Rain down a incredible amount of metal rods

firing line.name: Firing Line
firing line.desc: The user spawn 5 gun behind them which will start firing at the target immediately.

reqs.from: Shares a cooldown with Metal Turret.

oxidizing rush.name: Oxidizing Rush
oxidizing rush.desc: Conjure metal swords and rush forward with them

metal fakeout.name: Metal Fakeout
metal fakeout.desc: Create a metal clone and appear behind your taget.

iron quills.name: Iron Quills
iron quills.desc: Conjure metal from within, impaling surrounding enemies.

metal ball.name: Metal Ball
metal ball.desc: Form yourself into a metal ball and rush forward.

metal turret.name: Metal Turret
metal turret.desc: An automated turret that fires at targets that cross its sight.

reqs.from: Shares a cooldown with Firing Line.

metal armament.name: Metal Armament
metal armament.desc: Coat both your body and sword in an ironlike and fluctuating iron-bits. While active, it will swing a Kyrscleave-like Greatsword upon m1 (with an interval of 3s).

iron slam.name: Iron Slam
iron slam.desc: Conjure a giant rod of metal and slam it down.

iron hug.name: Iron Hug
iron hug.desc: Grab your opponent and crush them with your ironclad grip.

rocket lance.name: Rocket Lance
rocket lance.desc: Create a lance, impale your opponent, and send them flying.

metal gatling.name: Metal Gatling
metal gatling.desc: A deadly rush of several metallic rods.

blood orb.name: Blood Orb
blood orb.desc: Release an amalgamation of your blood.

bloodedge.name: Bloodedge
bloodedge.desc: Conjure a scythe of blood and swing.

vicious descent.name: Vicious Descent
vicious descent.desc: Leap into the air and slam down with vengeance.

sanguine dive.name: Sanguine Dive
sanguine dive.desc: Create or jump into a pool of blood.

reqs.from: Shares a cooldown with Beast Burrow and Shade Step

soulflare siphon.name: Soulflare Siphon
soulflare siphon.desc: Grab and siphon the blood out of your victim.

crimson rain.name: Crimson Rain
crimson rain.desc: Release blood daggers. Recast to recall them.

veinbreaker.name: Veinbreaker
veinbreaker.desc: Charge up a strong punch infused with your blood.

razor blitz.name: Razor Blitz
razor blitz.desc: Create weapons on your arms and dash through.

crimson surge.name: Crimson Surge
crimson surge.desc: Slash upwards and launch slashes of blood.

bloodcurdle.name: Bloodcurdle
bloodcurdle.desc: Manipulate the blood within your target's body.

bloodtide ritual.name: Bloodtide Ritual
bloodtide ritual.desc: Summon the Bloodtide and perform a sacrificial judgement.

permafrost prison.name: Permafrost Prison
permafrost prison.desc: Imprison your enemies with shadows and impale them with pillars of ice.

iron tether.name: Iron Tether
iron tether.desc: Summon two cubes tethered by lightning, setting a trap for your enemies.

tempest blitz.name: Tempest Blitz
tempest blitz.desc: Sprint forward on the winds themselves and deliver a devastating thunder kick.

flashfire sweep.name: Flashfire Sweep
flashfire sweep.desc: Sweep with flames and lightning before following into a devastating uppercut.

soul beam.name: Soul Beam
soul beam.desc: Harness the Chorus of Wisps to unleash a devastating blast.

reqs.from: Chorus of Souls, Oath: Oathless, Resonance

ether barrage.name: Ether Barrage
ether barrage.desc: Conjure concentrated orbs of Ether to launch at your enemy.

sing.name: Sing
sing.desc: Charm those around you with your powerful voice.

taunt.name: Taunt
taunt.desc: Taunt those around you, causing them to be unable to jump and to take more damage. However, in their rage they do extra damage.

dread whisper.name: Dread Whisper
dread whisper.desc: Grab your opponent and whisper a terrible truth in their ear. Further truths are unbearable. Deals increased damage to the insane.

glare.name: Glare
glare.desc: Opponents facing you are briefly rendered immobile.

exhaustion strike.name: Exhaustion Strike
exhaustion strike.desc: Execute a quick strike, emptying your posture when landed.

rally.name: Rally
rally.desc: Strike your shield a few times to absorb some of the posture received by your allies.

shoulder bash.name: Shoulder Bash
shoulder bash.desc: Rush at your enemies with full physical force.

reinforce.name: Reinforce
reinforce.desc: Buff those around you with extra defense and damage.

brace.name: Brace
brace.desc: Brace yourself against attacks and gain hyperarmour.

pressure blast.name: Pressure Blast
pressure blast.desc: Unleash a powerful pressure blast from the weight of your weapon.

punishment.name: Punishment
punishment.desc: Absorb damage then return fury upon your foes.

onslaught.name: Onslaught
onslaught.desc: Reel back and swing your weapon, unleashing an onslaught of blows if it hits.

neural pathway.name: Neural Pathway
neural pathway.desc: Using your mind's eye, you force your imagined position into reality, appearing to teleport a short distance. You alone know that the world moved, not you.

summon cauldron.name: Summon Cauldron
summon cauldron.desc: Make a cauldron appear from your memories.

prediction.name: Prediction
prediction.desc: Predict an opponent's attack and reflect it.

karita divebomb.name: Karita Divebomb
karita divebomb.desc: Launch into the air and deliver a devastating divebomb kick. Chains from Karita Leap.

rapid slashes.name: Rapid Slashes
rapid slashes.desc: Rush down your opponent cutting them apart.

ceaseless slashes.name: Ceaseless Slashes
ceaseless slashes.desc: Click to reveal yourself and deliver a rapid flurry of slashes that can chain together.

karita leap.name: Karita Leap
karita leap.desc: Launch yourself into a flying kick, backflipping you into the air if you hit a wall.

tacet drop kick.name: Tacet Drop Kick
tacet drop kick.desc: [Jus Karita] Disguise yourself in tacet and drop kick your enemies.

master's flourish.name: Master's Flourish
master's flourish.desc: A powerful slash that chips through block and slashes through armor.

prominence draw.name: Prominence Draw
prominence draw.desc: Close the distance and deliver a fast slash.

twincleave.name: Twincleave
twincleave.desc: Dart around the battlefield with devastating cleaves delivered in quick succesion.

flashdraw strike.name: Flashdraw Strike
flashdraw strike.desc: Swiftly unsheathe your blade and deliver an upwards strike.

slice 'n' dice.name: Slice 'n' Dice
slice 'n' dice.desc: Step forward and slice through your enemies. Ability can be activated again on successful hit.

strong left.name: Strong Left
strong left.desc: A powerful, flinging punch that shatters the air.

reqs.from: Shares a cooldown with Eclipse Kick.

rapid punches.name: Rapid Punches
rapid punches.desc: Unleash a barrage of blows against your foes.

table flip.name: Table Flip
table flip.desc: Toss the ground infront of you.

strong leap.name: Strong Leap
strong leap.desc: Kick off of the ground with your strength, sending you into the air.

skyshatter kick.name: Skyshatter Kick
skyshatter kick.desc: Unleash two devasting kicks with your brute strength.

pumpkin pitch.name: Pumpkin Pitch
pumpkin pitch.desc: Lob explosive pumpkins at your foes. Note: Requires Hallowtide '23 Seasonal Medal.

dread breath.name: Dread Breath
dread breath.desc: Channels the song through the power of the Dread Serpent.

mecha gatling.name: Mecha Gatling
mecha gatling.desc: Let loose a torrent of bullets from your shoulder mounted minigun.

whirling blade.name: Whirling Blade
whirling blade.desc: A chitinous scythe to cut through your foes in a whirl.

abyssal ridge.name: Abyssal Ridge
abyssal ridge.desc: Send a cascading eruption towards your foes, forcing them to react.

beast burrow.name: Beast Burrow
beast burrow.desc: Burrow underneath the ground before bursting out, knocking enemies up.

reqs.from: Monster Mantra, Shares a cooldown with Shade Step and Sanguine Dive

arc suit.name: Arc Suit
arc suit.desc: Encases the user in a durable armor.

arc beam.name: Arc Beam
arc beam.desc: Shoot out a laser from your eyes that explodes after a second, dealing fire and lightning damage.

arc wave.name: Arc Wave
arc wave.desc: Release a wave of energy around you, dealing fire and lightning damage.

mindsoothe.name: Mindsoothe
mindsoothe.desc: Heal nearby Players at the cost of your Sanity.

tranquil circle.name: Tranquil Circle
tranquil circle.desc: Disables mantras from being used, gives 10% Monster Armour and also gain total immunity to mantras whilst inside the radius.

sightless beam.name: Sightless Beam
sightless beam.desc: Fires a high pressure beam from your eyes.

sovereign drive.name: Sovereign Drive
sovereign drive.desc: Looking for details on this Mantra. Please ping @itsatelo in the Deepwoken Builder Discord!

skycrash.name: Skycrash
skycrash.desc: Looking for details on this Talent. Please ping @itsatelo in the Deepwoken Builder Discord!

warp kick.name: Warp Kick
warp kick.desc: Looking for details on this Talent. Please ping @itsatelo in the Deepwoken Builder Discord!

judgement.name: Judgement
judgement.desc: Summons a black casting circle before enveloping your target in black tendrils and tearing them apart.

lord's slice.name: Lord's Slice
lord's slice.desc: Makes the Hidden Tendril from 'Hidden Tendril' contract, pulling both the user and enemy closer.

equalizer.name: Equalizer
equalizer.desc: A counter that leaves your opponent open

blinding dawn.name: Blinding Dawn
blinding dawn.desc: Dance uncontrollably. No one can withstand the sheer groove of your spin routine.

radiant dawn.name: Radiant Dawn
radiant dawn.desc: Strike down your foes with your blinding light.

radiant kick.name: Radiant Kick
radiant kick.desc: Kick your foes at the speed of light.

close shave.name: Close Shave
close shave.desc: Close the distance and deliver a fast slash.

symbiotic sustain.name: Symbiotic Sustain
symbiotic sustain.desc: If linked to an ally, this move will take ~5% of your health and then heal your ally by that times an undefined amount.

parasitic leech.name: Parasitic Leech
parasitic leech.desc: If linked to an enemy, this move will start leeching your opponent's health for a few seconds while healing you.

blade of saints.name: Blade of Saints
blade of saints.desc: Conjure a blade attack depending on your Saint Stance.

ascension.name: Ascension
ascension.desc: Take to the skies for a devastating strike.

celestial assault.name: Celestial Assault
celestial assault.desc: Use your wings and deliver two critical blows.

sinister halo.name: Sinister Halo
sinister halo.desc: Emit a spinning halo of celestial energy, trapping and shredding all caught within its wake.

illusory counter.name: Illusory Counter
illusory counter.desc: If hit during the pose, negate the attacks and teleport the user behind the attacker.

illusory servants.name: Illusory Servants
illusory servants.desc: Spawns an illusion of yourself that targets the closest player.

mirror illusion.name: Mirror Illusion
mirror illusion.desc: Mirror your opponents and use their arsenal to your advantage.

jet kick.name: Jet Kick
jet kick.desc: Rush forward with a jet kick. Requires a target if you're in combat.

fake strike.name: Fake Strike
fake strike.desc: Trick your opponent and quickly go behind them.

restrain.name: Restrain
restrain.desc: Deliver a powerful kick that binds your opponent's soul to yours.

rupture.name: Rupture
rupture.desc: Detonate your chained target, unleashing a powerful blast that shatters their restraints and inflicts significant damage.

impel.name: Impel
impel.desc: Blast through your opponent's guard and pull them towards you.

palm strike.name: Palm Strike
palm strike.desc: Strike your opponent with your palm. If your true power is revealed, slice them up into the air.

decimate.name: Decimate
decimate.desc: Cut through your opponent, if True Strength is active, this attack will extend to nearby enemies. Fists cannot use this mantra. Autogrips players if low enough or knocked.

lethal injection.name: Lethal Injection
lethal injection.desc: Inject all of your readied Autobrews into your target. This might sting.

ardour slicer.name: Ardour Slicer
ardour slicer.desc: Close the distance and deliver a fast slash using your Ardour.

tacet kick.name: Tacet Kick
tacet kick.desc: Slip out of perception and deliver a brutal kick.
